SELECT
    FIELDS(ALL)
FROM
    Account
WHERE
    Name = 'GitLab'

SELECT FIELDS(ALL)
FROM AccountTeamMember
WHERE AccountId = '{{41.Id}}' 
    AND TeamMemberRole IN ('Integromat Owner', 'Integromat Solution Engineer')

SELECT
    FIELDS(ALL)
FROM
    CONTACT
WHERE
    ACCOUNTID = '{{48.`__IMTKEY__`}}'
